 water' when they mean that their loyalty to their family is greater than their loyalty to anyone else.\nFamilies have their problems and jealousies, but blood is thicker than water.", '血浓于水；家人总比外人亲\n家家有本难念的经，也都难免互生嫉妒，但总归血浓于水。']]}]